bstituted for the source provisions for consistency in the revised title and to eliminate unnecessary and obsolete language.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (c)(1), before clause (A), the words “and not contrary to law” are omitted as unnecessary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (c)(2), the words “and manage” and “and concerns” are omitted as unnecessary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (c)(3), the words “occasioned by death, resignation, or otherwise” are omitted as unnecessary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
